Trade the concession of that per-bond box into T (carry-in: enter on P2/P1, exit on T).

Tier 2 ‚Äî Heuristic (when you need a quick map)

Use a simple mapping by tenor bucket:

Short (‚â§5y): 5s2s (= ASW5 ‚àí ASW2)

Belly (‚âà7‚Äì10y): 10s2s (or 10s5s if 2y is noisy)

Long (‚â•20y): 30s10s

This is coarser (doesn‚Äôt adapt per bond), but easy to run as a benchmark.

How to verify you picked the right box (sanity checks)

High beta, small residual: regress 
