Why this is the right signal

It‚Äôs per bond (uses that bond‚Äôs ASW minus its own pillar benchmark).

It targets concession into T (P2/P1 vs T‚àí5), not post-auction moves.

It‚Äôs directional in the box, not the broad curve (level/slope neutralized by the benchmark).

