Great question ‚Äî once you extend the pre-auction window to 8 trading days you have to be careful not to peek into the future when forming the signal on the early days (P‚àí8, P‚àí7, P‚àí6). Here‚Äôs how to do it cleanly, plus drop-in code.

The core issue

Your earlier signal used concession vs T‚àí5.

That‚Äôs fine for entries at P‚àí2 / P‚àí1, because T‚àí5 is already known then.

But if you want to enter as early as P‚àí8, using ‚Äúvs T‚àí5‚Äù is look-ahead (T‚àí5 happens after P‚àí8).

