‚ÄúP&L is the box change from entry to T (in bp) minus costs; the equity curve is plotted by exit (auction) date, so it‚Äôs step-like because we don‚Äôt trade every day.‚Äù

Variants you can test quickly

Keep baseline T‚àí5 but restrict entries to 
[
‚àí
5
,
‚àí
1
]
[‚àí5,‚àí1] (no look-ahead, but a 5-day window, not 8).

